<refsect1 id='description'>
  <title>DESCRIPTION</title>

  <refsect2 id='decimal_prefixes'>
    <title>Decimal prefixes</title>

    <para>
      The SI system of units uses prefixes that indicate powers of
      ten.  A kilometer is 1000 meter, and a megawatt is 1000000 watt.
      Below the standard prefixes.
    </para>
