    <para>
      The symbol for micro is the Greek letter mu (µ), often written u
      in an ASCII context where this Greek letter is not available.  See
      also: <ulink
      url='http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/Units/prefixes.html'>http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/Units/prefixes.html</ulink>
    </para>

